Parts of Speech (Nouns, Verbs, Adjectives, etc.)
Each sentence has highlighted parts of speech:
✅ Noun: The manager scheduled a meeting(o)
✅ Verb: She completed the report on time.
✅ Adjective: We need a detailed analysis of sales figures.
✅ Adverb: He responded quickly to the email.
✅ Preposition: The documents are on the desk.
✅ Conjunction: I will finish this report before the deadline, but I need more data.
✅ Pronoun: She will handle the presentation tomorrow.
________________________________________
2. Basic Sentence Formation (S + V + O)
